## 2. Sequence Diagram (Message Flow)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    title Message Flow - AUTO_JOIN Event

    participant CC as 🟠 Class-Control App
    participant Redis as 🔴 Redis Stream<br/>(CLASSROOM_EVENTS)
    participant P1 as 🟢 Pod 1<br/>(device-control)
    participant P2 as 🟢 Pod 2<br/>(device-control)
    participant P3 as 🟢 Pod 3<br/>(device-control)
    participant S1 as 🔵 Student s1<br/>(on Pod 1)
    participant S7 as 🔵 Student s7<br/>(on Pod 2)

    rect rgb(255, 243, 205)
        Note over CC,Redis: Event Publishing
        CC->>Redis: XADD classroom_events * payload<br/>{"eventType":"AUTO_JOIN",<br/>"studentIds":["s1","s7"],<br/>"classId":"ee78ccf3-..."}
    end

    rect rgb(204, 229, 255)
        Note over Redis,P3: Fan-Out to All Pods
        Redis->>P1: Deliver event (studentIds: [s1, s7])
        Redis->>P2: Deliver event (studentIds: [s1, s7])
        Redis->>P3: Deliver event (studentIds: [s1, s7])
    end

    rect rgb(212, 237, 218)
        Note over P1,S1: Pod 1 Processing
        P1->>P1: Check activeSessions for "s1"
        Note right of P1: ✅ s1 FOUND
        P1->>S1: Send WebSocket Message (AUTO_JOIN)
        P1->>P1: Check activeSessions for "s7"
        Note right of P1: ❌ s7 NOT FOUND → Skip
    end

    rect rgb(212, 237, 218)
        Note over P2,S7: Pod 2 Processing
        P2->>P2: Check activeSessions for "s1"
        Note right of P2: ❌ s1 NOT FOUND → Skip
        P2->>P2: Check activeSessions for "s7"
        Note right of P2: ✅ s7 FOUND
        P2->>S7: Send WebSocket Message (AUTO_JOIN)
    end

    rect rgb(248, 215, 218)
        Note over P3: Pod 3 Processing
        P3->>P3: Check activeSessions for "s1"
        Note right of P3: ❌ s1 NOT FOUND → Skip
        P3->>P3: Check activeSessions for "s7"
        Note right of P3: ❌ s7 NOT FOUND → Skip
    end
```

