## 3. Component Diagram (Inside a Pod)

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph DeviceControlPod["🟢 Device-Control Pod"]
        direction TB

        subgraph WSLayer["WebSocket Layer"]
            WSEndpoint["🔌 WebSocket Endpoint<br/>(accepts WS connections)"]
        end

        subgraph SessionLayer["Session Management"]
            SessionMgr["📋 Session Manager"]
            SessionMap[("activeSessions<br/>Map&lt;String, WebSocketSession&gt;")]
        end

        subgraph ConsumerLayer["Redis Consumer Layer"]
            RedisConsumer["📡 Redis Stream Consumer<br/>(listens to CLASSROOM_EVENTS)"]
        end

        subgraph DispatchLayer["Dispatch Layer"]
            Dispatcher["📤 Message Dispatcher"]
        end

        WSEndpoint -->|"onConnect()<br/>register session"| SessionMgr
        WSEndpoint -->|"onDisconnect()<br/>remove session"| SessionMgr
        SessionMgr --> SessionMap

        RedisConsumer -->|"parsed event<br/>with studentIds[]"| Dispatcher
        Dispatcher -->|"lookup each<br/>studentId"| SessionMap
        Dispatcher -->|"send WS message<br/>(if session exists)"| WSEndpoint
    end

    NLB["🔀 NLB"] -->|"WS Connection"| WSEndpoint
    Redis[("🔴 Redis Stream")] -->|"XREAD"| RedisConsumer

    style DeviceControlPod fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745
    style WSLayer fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#66bb6a
    style SessionLayer fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#66bb6a
    style ConsumerLayer fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#66bb6a
    style DispatchLayer fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#66bb6a
```

