## 4. Activity/Flowchart Diagram (Pod Consumer Logic)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A([🚀 Start]) --> B["Receive event from<br/>Redis Stream<br/>(CLASSROOM_EVENTS)"]
    B --> C["Parse event payload"]
    C --> D["Extract studentIds[]<br/>from event"]
    D --> E{"More studentIds<br/>to process?"}

    E -->|"Yes"| F["Get next studentId"]
    F --> G{"studentId exists in<br/>activeSessions map?"}

    G -->|"Yes ✅"| H["Get WebSocketSession<br/>from map"]
    H --> I{"Session is open?"}

    I -->|"Yes ✅"| J["✉️ Send WebSocket<br/>message to student"]
    J --> K["✅ Message Delivered"]
    K --> E

    I -->|"No ❌"| L["Remove stale session<br/>from activeSessions"]
    L --> M["❌ Session Closed"]
    M --> E

    G -->|"No ❌"| N["⏭️ Student not on<br/>this pod → Skip"]
    N --> E

    E -->|"No"| O["Acknowledge message<br/>in Redis Stream"]
    O --> P([🏁 End])

    style A fill:#4caf50,color:#fff
    style P fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style J fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style K fill:#a5d6a7,stroke:#2e7d32
    style L fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#c62828
    style M fill:#ef9a9a,stroke:#c62828
    style N fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f9a825
```

