## 7. State Diagram (WebSocket Session Lifecycle)

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Connecting : Client initiates WS

    Connecting --> Connected : WS handshake success
    Connecting --> Failed : Handshake failed

    Connected --> Registered : Added to activeSessions map
    Registered --> ReceivingMessages : Redis event matches studentId

    ReceivingMessages --> ReceivingMessages : More events arrive
    ReceivingMessages --> Disconnecting : Client disconnects

    Registered --> Disconnecting : Client disconnects
    Registered --> Stale : Connection lost silently

    Stale --> Removed : Detected during dispatch
    Disconnecting --> Removed : onDisconnect() fired
    Removed --> [*] : Session cleaned up

    Failed --> [*]
```

