## 8. Redis Stream Event Structure

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class ClassroomEvent {
        +String eventType
        +String senderId
        +List~String~ studentIds
        +String classId
        +String participationCode
    }

    class RedisStream {
        +String streamName = "CLASSROOM_EVENTS"
        +xadd(payload) messageId
        +xread(count, block) List~Message~
        +xreadgroup(group, consumer) List~Message~
    }

    class DeviceControlPod {
        +Map~String_WebSocketSession~ activeSessions
        +onConnect(session) void
        +onDisconnect(sessionId) void
        +onStreamEvent(event) void
        +dispatchToLocal(studentId, message) void
    }

    class ClassControlApp {
        +publishEvent(event) void
    }

    ClassControlApp --> RedisStream : XADD
    RedisStream --> DeviceControlPod : XREAD
    DeviceControlPod --> ClassroomEvent : parses
```

